{
  "stem": "17761.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 153.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he studied with him [NON-ENGLISH], which is slaughtering, ritual slaughtering; [NON-ENGLISH], which is to be a mohel, and he had also a wonderful voice and knew a lot of how to pray Jewish prayers, how liturgical prayers in-- in-- in Jewish holidays and Shabbat and so on, so he had something in hand to make a living.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we left this village and we went to a small city in Bessarabia called Sculeni, S-C-U-L-E-N-I.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he found there a position, simply.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was not happy there, because there was no-- there were very few people religious in that community.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for my father, the education of his children, that was the most important thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he felt that we cannot get the appropriate education there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So about a year later, we left this community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the way, in Borough Park, there is Rabbi Yisroel from Sculeni, the Sculeni rabbi.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we studied together in cheder in Sculeni.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just visit him a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was very astonished to see me there, but he remembered me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He remembered my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very moved, because, you know, we were only three children in that cheder, the rabbi, my late brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the teachers were his father and my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the cheder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you know, it was very moving to see him again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there we went into a place in Moldova called Bracesdi, B-R-A-C-E-S-D-I, which was a bigger community.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father had there a nicer salary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there he had also a synagogue to be hazzan, which he did not have in Sculeni.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there we stayed for about two years and something.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
